img/portfolioImages/tryjquery.png.name: Try jQuery
img/portfolioImages/tryjquery.png.description: Try jQuery Interpreter Project. A project that was started by me at the Techrangers in 2012, but was put on the back burner in early 2013. It was built using jQuery to teach users jQuery. The interpreter works, but the tutorial was never finished.

img/portfolioImages/galacticlacquer.png.name: Galactic Lacquer
img/portfolioImages/galacticlacquer.png.description: My personal blog, Galactic Lacquer. I focus on nail art, nail polish, and makeup reviews. I heavily modified the Blogger template and created all of my own graphics. I also take and edit all of my own photos, and manage several social media pages for the blog. I also maintain several PR relationships as well.

img/portfolioImages/galacticlacquer.png.name: Techranger Team Site Redesign
img/portfolioImages/galacticlacquer.png.description: I am the project lead on the current redesign of the Techranger team website. Everything has been made from scratch utilizing HTML5, CSS3, and PHP. I created the bulk of the code while updating an existing design that someone had mocked up in Photoshop a couple years ago.
